description:
This week we grill the host of podcast "So Shameless" new author Passport Cutty! The ladies get Cutty to discuss how 60 mins of sex earned her $50,000, weeding out "johns" on sugar daddy sites, why guys love the damsel in distress and what exactly is a gold digger.
